{"tid":2106201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共清洗中小學圖書館  禁《動物農莊》","createTime":"2020-07-13T07:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T08:22:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7533d4010d1cd5909b4d44b2a049193636ccc1","tid":2106201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200713/O33NJV7LIS535RLMNAT234QFEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200713%2FO33NJV7LIS535RLMNAT234QFEA%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=2290c685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200713%2FO33NJV7LIS535RLMNAT234QFEA%2F&h=0385120a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200713/O33NJV7LIS535RLMNAT234QFEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共清洗中小學圖書館 <br />\n禁《動物農莊》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/urfkTBt6ReblC46atFEb_cIa8PE=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QB6AJBSN6ODMMDUP5W3EOU2LKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FurfkTBt6ReblC46atFEb_cIa8PE%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQB6AJBSN6ODMMDUP5W3EOU2LKE.jpg&h=fd1923b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧威爾的著作被中國封殺。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，中國為推習近平式愛國主義教育和純淨意識形態，要求全國中小學清理圖書館的「非法」和「不適宜」圖書，包括「危害國家統一、主權和領土完整」的書籍，《動物農莊》、《1984》和宗教圖書都牽涉其中，據報需清理書籍達數十萬冊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《小熊維尼》成推薦書<br />\n<br />\n報道特別提到，習近平治下，審查並非新鮮事，但是如此全國清理圖書館館藏的運動，讓人聯想文革時毛澤東驅使人民銷毀書籍；又提及早前香港政府要求公共圖書館下架黃<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n並需填寫表格上報。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，從去年10月教育部發通知起，全國至少有30間學校審查了圖書館館藏。該通知指明，「非法」圖書包括「擾亂社會秩<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n括《小熊維尼》，早前卡通角色小熊維尼被指貌似習近平而遭封殺，相關電影也未能在中國上映。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"58ca1c45d47701eec581c45b6b57f653e5851e18","tid":2106201,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c0e134616b06285e19cb0851155f969a0889a9","tid":2106201,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"琴獸農莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dfd0c0b20c88a43f218875ed4fdc2cdcb786d2","tid":2106201,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e4c031d97def53eeddb857d21d830d7fee04d014","tid":2106201,"uid":67292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:20:57.000Z","msg":"All animals are equal, but some animals are more equal than others. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n串到共產黨仆街。"},{"pid":"48505e897e7bf67fdaaa7c1549333566ca053326","tid":2106201,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}